{"id":40,"parent_id":0,"book_id":80,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":40,"title":"Chapter 37: Nephi and Lehi in Prison","subtitle":"","short_title":"Chapter 37","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison","content":[["div",{"id":"container","role":"main"},["div",{"type":"chapter","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison"},[".heading",{"id":"head1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.head1"},[".titleNumber","Chapter 37"],["h1","Nephi and Lehi in Prison"]],[".bodyBlock",[".image",{"id":"f1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.f1"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_040_01.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p3"},"Nephi and Lehi were Helaman’s sons. Helaman wanted them to be righteous like the Lehi and Nephi who left Jerusalem."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p4"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/5.4-7"},"Helaman 5:4–7"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f2","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.f2"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_040_02.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p5"},"Helaman taught his sons to believe in Jesus Christ. They learned that forgiveness comes through faith and repentance."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p6"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/5.9-12"},"Helaman 5:9–12"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.f3"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_040_03.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p7"},"Nephi and Lehi went to teach the word of God to the Nephites and Lamanites. Thousands of people were baptized."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p8"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/5.14-19"},"Helaman 5:14–19"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.f4"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_040_04.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p9"},"When Nephi and Lehi went to the land of Nephi, a Lamanite army threw them into prison and did not give them food for many days."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p10"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/5.20-22"},"Helaman 5:20–22"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.f5"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_040_05.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p11"},"The Lamanites went to the prison to kill Nephi and Lehi but could not because they were protected by a ring of fire that would have burned anyone who tried to touch them."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p12","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p12"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/5.22-23"},"Helaman 5:22–23"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.f6"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_040_06.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p13","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p13"},"Nephi and Lehi were not burned by the fire. They told the Lamanites that God’s power was protecting them."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p14","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p14"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/5.24-26"},"Helaman 5:24–26"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.f7"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_040_07.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p15","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p15"},"The ground and the prison walls began to shake. A dark cloud surrounded the people in the prison, and they were afraid."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p16","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p16"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/5.27-28"},"Helaman 5:27–28"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.f8"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_040_08.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p17","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p17"},"A voice from above the darkness spoke. It was quiet like a whisper, but everyone could hear it."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p18","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p18"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/5.29-30"},"Helaman 5:29–30"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.f9"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_040_09.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p19","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p19"},"The voice told the people to repent and stop trying to kill Nephi and Lehi."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p20","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p20"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/5.29-30"},"Helaman 5:29–30"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.f10"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_040_10.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p21","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p21"},"The voice spoke three times, and the ground and prison walls continued to shake. The Lamanites could not run away because it was too dark and they were too scared."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p22","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p22"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/5.33-34"},"Helaman 5:33–34"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.f11"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_040_11.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p23","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p23"},"A Nephite who had been a Church member saw that Nephi’s and Lehi’s faces were shining through the darkness."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p24","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p24"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/5.35-36"},"Helaman 5:35–36"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f12","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.f12"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_040_12.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p25","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p25"},"Nephi and Lehi were looking toward heaven and talking. The man told the Lamanites to look. They wondered whom Nephi and Lehi were talking to."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p26","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p26"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/5.36-38"},"Helaman 5:36–38"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f13","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.f13"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_040_13.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p27","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p27"},"The man, who was named Aminadab, told the Lamanites that Nephi and Lehi were talking to angels."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p28","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p28"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/5.39"},"Helaman 5:39"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f14","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.f14"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_040_14.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p29","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p29"},"The Lamanites asked Aminadab how to get rid of the dark cloud. He told them to repent and pray until they had faith in Jesus Christ."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p30","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p30"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/5.40-41"},"Helaman 5:40–41"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f15","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.f15"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_040_15.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p31","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p31"},"The Lamanites prayed until the dark cloud was gone."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p32","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p32"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/5.42"},"Helaman 5:42"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f16","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.f16"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_040_16.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p33","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p33"},"When the darkness left, the people saw a pillar of fire all around them. The fire did not burn them or the prison walls."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p34","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p34"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/5.43-44"},"Helaman 5:43–44"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f17","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.f17"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_040_17.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p35","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p35"},"The Lamanites felt great joy, and the Spirit of God filled their hearts."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p36","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p36"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/5.44-45"},"Helaman 5:44–45"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f18","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.f18"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_040_18.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p37","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p37"},"A voice whispered, saying they would be comforted because of their faith in Jesus Christ."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p38","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p38"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/5.46-47"},"Helaman 5:46–47"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f19","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.f19"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_040_19.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p39","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p39"},"The Lamanites looked up to see where the voice had come from. They saw angels coming down from heaven."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p40","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p40"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/5.48"},"Helaman 5:48"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f20","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.f20"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_040_20.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p41","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p41"},"About 300 people saw and heard what happened in the prison. They went and told others."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p42","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p42"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/5.49-50"},"Helaman 5:49–50"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f21","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.f21"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_040_21.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p43","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p43"},"Most of the Lamanites believed them and put away their weapons."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p44","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p44"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/5.50-51"},"Helaman 5:50–51"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f22","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.f22"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_040_22.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p45","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p45"},"The Lamanites stopped hating the Nephites and gave back the land they had taken. The Lamanites became more righteous than the Nephites."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p46","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p46"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/5.50,52"},"Helaman 5:50, 52"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f23","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.f23"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_040_23.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p47","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p47"},"Many Lamanites went with Nephi and Lehi and taught both Nephites and Lamanites."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p48","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-37-nephi-and-lehi-in-prison.p48"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/6.1,6-7"},"Helaman 6:1, 6–7"]]]]]]]],"refs":null}
